---
title: "US48 — Upload / manage expert content"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ServicesScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>PublishService + SendDeliverable
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>StorageGateway + SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: upload content file / media
  B->>C: attach(content)
  C->>G: upload to Storage, link in deliverables
  G-->>C: url
  C-->>B: content available
  B-->>A: clients can access it
  note over B,G: scope under review (reconciliation log)
